## Docker commands used to build the application 
# docker build -t udacity-techtrends -f ./techtrends/Dockerfile .

## Docker commands used to run the application
# docker run --rm -d -p 7111:3111/tcp --name udacity-techtrends-container udacity-techtrends

## The command to kill the container
# docker stop  udacity-techtrends-container 

## Docker commands used to get the application logs
# docker logs -f udacity-techtrends-container

